---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Now">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Now</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2026</p>

    <p>
      This is my <a href="https://nownownow.com/about" target="_blank">now page</a>,
      a snapshot of what I'm focused on at this point in my life.
    </p>

    <h2>Making</h2>
    <p>
      I'm building <a href="https://contentboo.st" target="_blank">contentboo.st</a>,
      a content creation tool. This is my main focus right now.
      I write about the process, the decisions, and what I learn along the way.
    </p>

    <h2>Learning</h2>
    <p>Currently deepening my understanding of:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Flutter & mobile development patterns</li>
      <li>Object-oriented design principles</li>
      <li>The craft of building products people actually want</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Reading</h2>
    <p>Flutter Engineering by Majid Hajian</p>

    <h2>Location</h2>
    <p>Digital nomad life. Currently based wherever the wifi is good.</p>

    <hr />

    <p>
      <em>
        Inspired by <a href="https://sive.rs/now" target="_blank">Derek Sivers</a>
        and the /now page movement.
      </em>
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .last-updated {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 0;
  }
</style>
